dBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T02:37:29.000Z","msg":"喺邊度可以學到呢d知識架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957c3a0f829578db6572f513aaa2fe955a66e961","tid":2458441,"uid":199637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"197b87ec76cb0ae00465b9b66d883a5d0225c7ce","tid":2458441,"uid":119609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T15:08:50.000Z","msg":"自從輸咗幾次long之後就轉玩short了，covered / cash secured 非常安全，跌市又可以蝕少啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T17:51:37.000Z","msg":"巴打上網學？"},{"pid":"4497c25e6bfd6f1332a78086181597699d427cad","tid":2458441,"uid":119609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"957c3a0f829578db6572f513aaa2fe955a66e961","tid":2458441,"uid":199637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"197b87ec76cb0ae00465b9b66d883a5d0225c7ce","tid":2458441,"uid":119609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T15:08:50.000Z","msg":"自從輸咗幾次long之後就轉玩short了，covered / cash secured 非常安全，跌市又可以蝕少啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T17:51:37.000Z","msg":"巴打上網學？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T23:46:18.000Z","msg":"輸得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始玩OTM Long, 雖然平（但啲大股都講緊可能要百幾鎂/幾百鎂一張），但股票升佢唔識升，股票妹佢仲會跌<br />\n<br />\n跟住玩ATM long, 但美市時間問題（而加夏令會好少少），一定要訓前set目標價賣，一係股票升千食唔到10倍，一係唔到賣價仲要跌返落去，以後都上唔返<br />\n<br />\nITM Leap 未試過，巴打話似揸正股<br />\n<br />\nShort 好處係中間可以用少啲時間睇市等到期<br />\n<br />\nCovered Short call strike 就永遠set 成本價高20-30% 當止賺出貨（其實有20-30%升幅對正常股市黎講係非常多）<br />\n<br />\nShort put 就set自己心目中個價就得，到期到價唔想接貨先roll<br />\n<br />\ntl;dr. 做short用少咗時間睇市"},{"pid":"1b93a829e011f382aaed0af7d9bcbc79e70c78ba","tid":2458441,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T23:52:31.000Z","msg":"有貨係手就Short 多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一邊等一邊袋少少飯錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}